  "text": "We hypothesized that due to its similarities to other behavioral addictions, SPD may also be associated with impairments of white matter fibers [CITATION_1] . In this study, we investigated white matter integrity in young adults with SPD using observer-independent tract-based spatial statistics (TBSS) analysis with DTI and linked the quantitative variables of brain structures to the behavioral measures of SPD.",
